19:11.025 --> 19:12.299
Look at me!

19:12.360 --> 19:14.635
I'm playing golf!

19:14.696 --> 19:16.379
(laughing)

19:16.439 --> 19:19.991
Rum-Ta-Tum, your time has come!

19:20.184 --> 19:21.534
RALPH:
Whee!

19:22.704 --> 19:24.495
(laughing)

19:24.688 --> 19:26.956
Class warfare!
(giggling)

19:31.487 --> 19:32.895
Bart Simpson,

19:32.914 --> 19:34.380
the next time
you want to make a point...

19:34.531 --> 19:38.567
(chuckles) I would prefer
you use your words.

19:38.628 --> 19:42.847
Did you honestly think a little
vandalism would shut<i> us</i> down?

19:42.998 --> 19:45.074
(chuckles)
Greens can be reseeded,

19:45.134 --> 19:48.427
traps re-sanded,
roughs unsmoothed.

19:48.521 --> 19:49.854
The club will go on.

19:50.005 --> 19:51.505
(siren wailing)

19:51.524 --> 19:55.151
Ah, and here are the police
to take you to jail.

19:56.687 --> 19:59.422
This is a raid!
We're closing the club down!

19:59.440 --> 20:01.273
