Me?

20:03.352 --> 20:05.928
But<i> they</i> are
the ne'er-do-wells.

20:05.988 --> 20:09.098
I am the head
of a legitimate religion.

20:09.116 --> 20:10.449
You sure are.

20:10.543 --> 20:13.118
